{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Please close your eyes,"},{"time":3000,"text":"and open your hands."},{"time":6000,"text":"Now imagine what you could place in your hands:"},{"time":9000,"text":"an apple, maybe your wallet."},{"time":12000,"text":"Now open your eyes."},{"time":14000,"text":"What about a life?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16000,"text":"What you see here is a premature baby."},{"time":18000,"text":"He looks like he's resting peacefully, but in fact he's struggling to stay alive"},{"time":21000,"text":"because he can't regulate his own body temperature."},{"time":24000,"text":"This baby is so tiny he doesn't have"},{"time":26000,"text":"enough fat on his body to stay warm."},{"time":28000,"text":"Sadly, 20 million babies like this"},{"time":31000,"text":"are born every year around the world."},{"time":34000,"text":"Four million of these babies die annually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"But the bigger problem is that the ones who do survive"},{"time":39000,"text":"grow up with severe, long-term health problems."},{"time":42000,"text":"The reason is because in the first month of a baby's life,"},{"time":45000,"text":"its only job is to grow."},{"time":47000,"text":"If it's battling hypothermia, its organs can't develop normally,"},{"time":50000,"text":"resulting in a range of health problems"},{"time":52000,"text":"from diabetes, to heart disease,"},{"time":54000,"text":"to low I.Q."},{"time":56000,"text":"Imagine: Many of these problems could be prevented"},{"time":59000,"text":"if these babies were just kept warm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62000,"text":"That is the primary function of an incubator."},{"time":64000,"text":"But traditional incubators require electricity"},{"time":66000,"text":"and cost up to 20 thousand dollars."},{"time":69000,"text":"So, you're not going to find them in rural areas of developing countries."},{"time":72000,"text":"As a result, parents resort to local solutions"},{"time":75000,"text":"like tying hot water bottles around their babies' bodies,"},{"time":78000,"text":"or placing them under light bulbs like the ones you see here --"},{"time":81000,"text":"methods that are both ineffective and unsafe."},{"time":84000,"text":"I've seen this firsthand over and over again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87000,"text":"On one of my first trips to India, I met this young woman, Sevitha,"},{"time":90000,"text":"who had just given birth to a tiny premature baby, Rani."},{"time":94000,"text":"She took her baby to the nearest village clinic,"},{"time":97000,"text":"and the doctor advised her to take Rani"},{"time":99000,"text":"to a city hospital so she could be placed in an incubator."},{"time":103000,"text":"But that hospital was over four hours away,"},{"time":106000,"text":"and Sevitha didn't have the means to get there,"},{"time":109000,"text":"so her baby died."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"Inspired by this story, and dozens of other similar stories like this,"},{"time":114000,"text":"my team and I realized what was needed was a local solution,"},{"time":117000,"text":"something that could work without electricity,"},{"time":119000,"text":"that was simple enough for a mother or a midwife to use,"},{"time":122000,"text":"given that the majority of births still take place in the home."},{"time":125000,"text":"We needed something that was portable,"},{"time":127000,"text":"something that could be sterilized and reused across multiple babies"},{"time":130000,"text":"and something ultra-low-cost,"},{"time":132000,"text":"compared to the 20,000 dollars"},{"time":134000,"text":"that an incubator in the U.S. costs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"So, this is what we came up with."},{"time":139000,"text":"What you see here looks nothing like an incubator."},{"time":141000,"text":"It looks like a small sleeping bag for a baby."},{"time":144000,"text":"You can open it up completely. It's waterproof."},{"time":147000,"text":"There's no seams inside so you can sterilize it very easily."},{"time":150000,"text":"But the magic is in this pouch of wax."},{"time":154000,"text":"This is a phase-change material."},{"time":156000,"text":"It's a wax-like substance with a melting point"},{"time":158000,"text":"of human body temperature, 37 degrees Celsius."},{"time":161000,"text":"You can melt this simply using hot water"},{"time":164000,"text":"and then when it melts it's able to maintain one constant temperature"},{"time":168000,"text":"for four to six hours at a time,"},{"time":170000,"text":"after which you simply reheat the pouch."},{"time":173000,"text":"So, you then place it into this little pocket back here,"},{"time":180000,"text":"and it creates a warm micro-environment"},{"time":182000,"text":"for the baby."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"Looks simple, but we've reiterated this dozens of times"},{"time":189000,"text":"by going into the field to talk to doctors, moms and clinicians"},{"time":192000,"text":"to ensure that this really meets the needs of the local communities."},{"time":195000,"text":"We plan to launch this product in India in 2010,"},{"time":198000,"text":"and the target price point will be 25 dollars,"},{"time":202000,"text":"less than 0.1 percent of the cost"},{"time":204000,"text":"of a traditional incubator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"Over the next five years we hope to save the lives"},{"time":209000,"text":"of almost a million babies."},{"time":211000,"text":"But the longer-term social impact is a reduction in population growth."},{"time":214000,"text":"This seems counterintuitive,"},{"time":216000,"text":"but turns out that as infant mortality is reduced,"},{"time":219000,"text":"population sizes also decrease,"},{"time":221000,"text":"because parents don't need to anticipate"},{"time":223000,"text":"that their babies are going to die."},{"time":225000,"text":"We hope that the Embrace infant warmer"},{"time":228000,"text":"and other simple innovations like this"},{"time":230000,"text":"represent a new trend for the future of technology:"},{"time":234000,"text":"simple, localized, affordable solutions"},{"time":237000,"text":"that have the potential to make huge social impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"In designing this we followed a few basic principles."},{"time":243000,"text":"We really tried to understand the end user,"},{"time":245000,"text":"in this case, people like Sevitha."},{"time":248000,"text":"We tried to understand the root of the problem"},{"time":250000,"text":"rather than being biased by what already exists."},{"time":253000,"text":"And then we thought of the most simple solution we could"},{"time":256000,"text":"to address this problem."},{"time":258000,"text":"In doing this, I believe we can truly bring technology to the masses."},{"time":262000,"text":"And we can save millions of lives through the simple warmth of an Embrace."}]}]}